 || [[Roberto Hern\u00e1ndez (relief pitcher)|Hern\u00e1ndez]] (31) || 20,715 || 82-74\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"ffbbbb\"\n| 157 || September 26 || @ [[Baltimore Orioles|Orioles]] || 2 \u2013 1 || [[Jos\u00e9 Mercedes|Mercedes]] (13-7) || '''[[David Wells|Wells]]''' (20-7) || [[Ryan Kohlmeier|Kohlmeier]] (13) || 31,614 || 82-75\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"bbffbb\"\n| 158 || September 27 || @ [[Baltimore Orioles|Orioles]] || 4 \u2013 0 || '''[[Frank Castillo|Castillo]]''' (10-5) || [[Sidney Ponson|Ponson]] (9-13) || || 30,362 || 83-75\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"ffbbbb\"\n| 159 || September 28 || @ [[Baltimore Orioles|Orioles]] || 23 \u2013 1 || [[Pat Rapp|Rapp]] (9-12) || '''[[Chris Carpenter|Carpenter]]''' (10-12) || || 32,203 || 83-76\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"ffbbbb\"\n| 160 || September 29 || @ [[Cleveland Indians|Indians]] || 8 \u2013 4 || [[Justin Speier|Speier]] (5-2) || '''[[Steve Trachsel|Trachsel]]''' (8-15) || [[Steve Karsay|Karsay]] (20) || 42,768 || 83-77\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"ffbbbb\"\n| 161 || September 30 || @ [[Cleveland Indians|Indians]] || 6 \u2013 5 || [[Chuck Finley|Finley]] (16-11) || '''[[Esteban Loaiza|Loaiza]]''' (10-13) || [[Bob Wickman|Wickman]] (14) || 42,676 || 83-78\n|}</div></div>\n|-\n|<div class=\"NavFrame\">\n<div class=\"NavHead\" style=\"background:#9EBD69; \">October</div>\n<div class=\"NavContent\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\n{| border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! bgcolor=\"#DDDDFF\" width=\"4%\" | #\n! bgcolor=\"#DDDDFF\" width=\"11%\" | Date\n! bgcolor=\"#DDDDFF\" width=\"11%\" | Opponent\n! bgcolor=\"#DDDDFF\" width=\"8%\" | Score\n! bgcolor=\"#DDDDFF\" width=\"14%\" | Win\n! bgcolor=\"#DDDDFF\" width=\"14%\" | Loss\n! bgcolor=\"#DDDDFF\" width=\"13%\" | Save\n! bgcolor=\"#DDDDFF\" width=\"10%\" | Attendance\n! bgcolor=\"#DDDDFF\" width=\"5%\" | Record\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"ffbbbb\"\n| 162 || October 1 || @ [[Cleveland Indians|Indians]] || 11 \u2013 4 